snippet.title: [Official Trailer] Veins Like Tapeworms
snippet.description:
While working at their dead-end job and dreaming of what could’ve been, Demian Zhao discovers a flesh-eating parasite who promises to help them finally live free. They can become the monster of your own making - after all, who needs a moral compass when you have a god in the gutter?

Wishlist on Steam now! Available February 14th, 2025.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3106780/Veins_Like_Tapeworms/
itch.io demo: https://awesometrinket.itch.io/demo-veins-like-tapeworms
